dmca.title: Notification of Claimed Infringement
dmca.body:
-----Original Message-----
From: Jason [mailto:chaos@voidgate.org] 
Posted At: Thursday, November 02, 2006 12:28 AM
Posted To: Copyright
Conversation: Notification of Claimed Infringement
Subject: Notification of Claimed Infringement


Hello Andrea Almeida,

You will find attached an official complaint of copyright infringement
against the website located at IP address 70.87.62.162
(www.baphomatty.com).  Madeline von Foerster owned baphomatty.com
through which she showcased her artwork via http://www.baphomatty.com
hosted at Voidgate Internetworks from March of 2001 until March of 2006,
around which time she changed her domain and hosting provider.  The
complaint involves infringing material in the form of several images of
paintings copyrighted by Madeline von Foerster, and displayed on the
website in question without her consent.  Please read the attached
notice for all the details.  Thank you for your time.

Sincerely,
Jason Colson
Voidgate Internetworks
